value.0: This stone seems to almost vibrate with ancient power.

Ajunta Pall, one of the oldest Sith Lords to have ever lived. This ancient statue, left to honor the memory of his strength, perfectly depicts him with lifelike design made all the more menacing by the notched sword held in his grasp. The sword appears to be separate from the statue, but alas, thousands of years of solitude have caused the grasp of this stone guardian to tighten, forever trapping the blade within its hand, until the day it is finally destroyed.
